FBIS4-41176 "drsov121_a_94026" FBIS-SOV-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Grachev Calls Strategic Nuclear Forces `Priority' Grachev Calls Strategic Nuclear Forces `Priority' LD2206124594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0900 GMT 22 Jun 94 LD2206124594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Excerpt] [passage omitted] In the opinion Defense Minister Pavel Grachev, the Strategic Nuclear Forces -- the Strategic Rocket forces, the Naval and Air Force strategic nuclear forces -- are a realistic guarantee of ensuring Russia's security in modern circumstances and will remain a major deterrent against war in the future. In the minister's opinion, the strategic nuclear forces will be a priority in the formation of the Russian Armed Forces.
